T1  - A Comparison of Heuristic and Optimum Solutions in Resource-Constrained Project Scheduling
AU  - Davis, Edward W.
AU  - Patterson, James H.
Y1  - 1975/04/01
PY  - 1975
DA  - 1975/04/01
