TY  - JOUR
T1  - The Science-Technology-Utilization Relationship in Management
AU  - Gruber, William H.
AU  - Niles, John S.
Y1  - 1975/04/01
PY  - 1975
DA  - 1975/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.21.8.956
